	Installation:
		Copy folders /res and /themes with one of the gara files to your desired
		location. Here's a legend of which gara files contains what:
		
			gara.js - Simply gara :)
			gara-c.js - gara + $class library
			gara-b.js - gara + base2 library
			gara-bc.js - gara + base2 + $class libraries
		
		If you are using one of the required libs in your application you may
		choose a file without the lib.
	
		
	Usage:
		Include the following files in your document:
		
			/res/gara-yui-reset-fonts.css
			/themes/[theme]/[theme].css
			/gara.js
			
		If you use YUI's reset and fonts, you can use gara.css instead.
